Class CUpti_ActivityDevice5

    @Properties(inherit=cupti.class)
public class CUpti_ActivityDevice5
extends Pointer
    \brief The activity record for a device. (CUDA 11.6 onwards) This activity record represents information about a GPU device (CUPTI_ACTIVITY_KIND_DEVICE).
